Our model solves  the hierarchy problem in a fashion very similar
to the models considered in, with
two concentric branes embedded in a noncompact bulk. In this
references, the hierarchy and the positions of the branes are
naturally stabilized by a generalization  of the
Goldberger and Wise mechanism (see also
